Class StockRecordParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • sql.StockRecordParam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Subscribable

    public class StockRecordParam
extends Object
implements Subscribable
    The parameters for the StockRecord request from the SQL database.

    Each field can have multiple parameters.
